title: Red Raiders take third at Thunderbird Collegiate - Texas Tech Red Raiders - TexasTech.com
content: Red Raiders take third at Thunderbird Collegiate - Texas Tech Red Raiders  TexasTech.com
description: Texas Tech finished third at Thunderbird Collegiate with Ludvig Aberg and Calum Scott both recording top-10 finishes to complete the regular season at the Papago Golf Course. The No. 7 Red Raiders posted a final round of 12-under to leap up the leaderboard during Saturday's final round before No. 1 Oklahoma pulled away to win the team championship.
